graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator Pod"
        Manager[Manager Controller]
        RayController[RayCluster Controller]
        AppWrapperController[AppWrapper Controller]
        MutatingWebhook[Mutating Webhook]
        ValidatingWebhook[Validating Webhook]
        CertController[Cert Controller]

        Manager -->|runs| RayController
        Manager -->|runs| AppWrapperController
        Manager -->|serves| MutatingWebhook
        Manager -->|serves| ValidatingWebhook
        Manager -->|manages certs| CertController
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
        AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources (per RayCluster)"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Deployment<br/>OpenShift]
        RayRoute[Route: ray-dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443 edge TLS]
        ClientRoute[Route: ray-client<br/>gRPC/10001 passthrough]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Head + Worker isolation]
        CertSecret["Secret: cluster-ca<br/>mTLS certificates"]
        Service[Services<br/>Dashboard + Client]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources (per AppWrapper)"
        WrappedResources[Grouped Resources<br/>Jobs, Deployments, etc.]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.2.1]
        Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.10.1+]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
        CertManager[cert-controller<br/>v0.12.0]
    end

    User[User/Notebook] -->|creates| RayClusterCR
    User -->|creates| AppWrapperCR

    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| RayController
    K8sAPI -->|validates via| ValidatingWebhook
    K8sAPI -->|mutates via| MutatingWebhook

    RayController -->|creates| OAuthProxy
    RayController -->|creates| RayRoute
    RayController -->|creates| ClientRoute
    RayController -->|creates| NetworkPolicy
    RayController -->|creates| CertSecret
    RayController -->|creates| Service

    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| AppWrapperController
    AppWrapperController -->|integrates with| Kueue
    AppWrapperController -->|creates when admitted| WrappedResources

    RayClusterCR -->|base management| KubeRay
    CertController -->|rotates certs via| CertManager

    Manager -->|watches/creates via| K8sAPI

    style Manager fill:#4a90e2
    style RayController fill:#4a90e2
    style AppWrapperController fill:#4a90e2
    style MutatingWebhook fill:#4a90e2
    style ValidatingWebhook fill:#4a90e2
    style RayClusterCR fill:#f5a623
    style AppWrapperCR fill:#f5a623
    style KubeRay fill:#999
    style Kueue fill:#999
    style CertManager fill:#999
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321
    style NetworkPolicy fill:#7ed321
